Package: wickrastrategyci
Type: Package
Title: Test Trading Strategies in CI
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-strategy-ci over its C ABI hub: create a
    Session, golden-pin a strategy's backtest report, assert tolerances and
    invariant properties, and fuzz-test against seeded data perturbations - the
    same protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-strategy-ci
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-strategy-ci/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-strategy-ci C ABI shared library (WKSTRATEGYCI_LIB)
    and its header (WKSTRATEGYCI_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
